<div class="content-section">
  <p>GetYourTester is a platform designed to connect product owners who need quality testing with skilled testers who can provide valuable feedback.</p>
  
  <h3>Our Mission</h3>
  <p>Our mission is to simplify the process of finding the right testers for your products, enabling better quality assurance and user experience improvements.</p>
  
  <h3>How It Works</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Product owners create listings for products that need testing</li>
    <li>Testers can browse and apply to test products that match their skills</li>
    <li>Product owners select suitable testers</li>
    <li>Testers provide feedback, bug reports, and suggestions</li>
    <li>Product owners use this feedback to improve their products</li>
  </ol>
  
  <h3>Our Team</h3>
  <p>We are a dedicated team of professionals passionate about improving product quality through effective testing.</p>
